      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously maintained E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, an atmospheric masterpiece with an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit is equipped with the 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission for lightning-fast shifts and the M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis is supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing adjustable damping rates to suit both spirited canyon runs and daily transit. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and new throttle actuators, ensuring mechanical longevity. The exterior retains its aerodynamic profile with functional heat extractors and a carbon fiber roof, while the interior features Novillo leather with minimal bolster wear. A mechanically sound example of BMW's final naturally aspirated M-car.",
